cond? does this solved the problem for you? if yes, i will change it. the solution from @butonic is definitely not wrong. i just wonder why the other solution works here too and want to make sure that this is really the issue on your system."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/22497828","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/4326#issuecomment-22497828","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4326","id":22497828,"user":{"login":"adonald","id":1714299,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/f38bbdcc5f23d5886721947e0b22f669?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fa2009e3846f10bd733ff0bb090c21acd.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"f38bbdcc5f23d5886721947e0b22f669","url":"https://api.github.com/users/adonald","html_url":"https://github.com/adonald","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/adonald/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/adonald/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/adonald/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/adonald/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/adonald/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/adonald/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/adonald/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/adonald/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/adonald/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-08-12t14:40:23z","updated_at":"2013-08-12t14:40:23z","body":"i have an installation of owncloud 5.0.9 with files_encryption enabled, and i also had the same error as @enoch85.\r\n\r\nafter a bit of grep in the apps/files_encryption/ directory, i found that apps/files_encryption/files/error.php did not have the same reference to /lib/base.php as every other file that required it.\r\n\r\nmost files had:\r\n```\r\nrequire_once realpath(dirname(__file__) . '/../../../lib/base.php');\r\n```\r\n\r\nerror.php had:\r\n```\r\nrequire_once '../../../lib/base.php';\r\n```\r\n\r\nreplacing the offending line in error.php with the line in the first code block has resolved the issue for me."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/22499057","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/4326#issuecomment-22499057","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4326","id":22499057,"user":{"login":"enoch85","id":4511254,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/a92cb070ca805f83a0fbd170b56f8f19?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f9a367e33a743f8dbdf52d500691a5eee.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"a92cb070ca805f83a0fbd170b56f8f19","url":"https://api.github.com/users/enoch85","html_url":"https://github.com/enoch85","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/enoch85/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/enoch85/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/enoch85/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/enoch85/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/enoch85/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/enoch85/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/enoch85/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/enoch85/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/enoch85/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-08-12t14:55:41z","updated_at":"2013-08-12t14:55:41z","body":"i will also try in a little while... update coming soon."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/22503520","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/4326#issuecomment-22503520","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4326","id":22503520,"user":{"login":"adonald","id":1714299,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/f38bbdcc5f23d5886721947e0b22f669?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fa2009e3846f10bd733ff0bb090c21acd.png&r=x","gravatar_id":